room_title: Escape room "The Composer" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description: As one of the most distinguished, and internationally renowned composers of music, Dr. Dubois, lived a life of passion and dedication to creating beautiful masterpieces, before his untimely death. You and your team, all former students of Dr. Dubois, must race against time to locate and rescue your beloved mentor's eighth, and final, sonata, before it is lost forever.
